oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Portrait of Clara Adeline "Addie" Goodwin Bradshaw (1861-1938), wife of John Bradshaw, and some of her children. Back row: Dora Bradshaw Cartwright (1892-1979) and Arthur F. Bradshaw (1889-1966). Front row: Ethel Kate Bradshaw (1894-1941) Sarah Estelle Bradshaw Kelley (1899-1993), and John William Bradshaw (1896-1991).
